<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Fiche Traitement Signable - {{ traitement.titre }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin: 20px;
            color: #333;
            background-color: white;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745, #20c997);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: white;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .header p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .info-section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .info-section h3 {
            color: #28a745;
            margin-top: 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .info-row {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 120px;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .suivi-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .suivi-table th {
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .suivi-table td {
            padding: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .suivi-table tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 2px solid #856404;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .signature-section h3 {
            color: #856404;
            margin-top: 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .signature-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .signature-block {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #856404;
            height: 40px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        .signature-line::before {
            content: "Signer ici";
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            color: #856404;
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 10px;
        }
        .date-field {
            border: 1px solid #856404;
            height: 25px;
            margin-top: 5px;
            background-color: white;
        }
        .validation-section {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .validation-section h4 {
            color: #155724;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .checkbox-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .checkbox-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #155724;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        .checkbox {
            width: 15px;
            height: 15px;
            border: 2px solid #155724;
            margin-right: 8px;
            background-color: white;
        }
        .observations-area {
            width: 100%;
            height: 60px;
            border: 1px solid #856404;
            margin-top: 10px;
            background-color: white;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #6c757d;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding-top: 15px;
        }
        .official-stamp {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border: 3px dashed #dc3545;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #dc3545;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 11px;
            transform: rotate(-15deg);
        }
        .page-break {
            page-break-before: always;
        }
        @media print {
            body {
                margin: 10px;
            }
            .signature-section {
                background-color: white;
                border: 2px solid #856404;
            }
            .validation-section {
                background-color: white;
                border: 1px solid #155724;
            }
            .official-stamp {
                border-color: #dc3545;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>FICHE TRAITEMENT SIGNABLE</h1>
        <p>{{ traitement.titre }}</p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px;">Document officiel - √Ä signer et conserver</p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-section">
        <h3>üìã INFORMATIONS DU TRAITEMENT</h3>
        <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Patient :</span>
            <span>{{ traitement.etudiant.fullName }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Psychologue :</span>
            <span>{{ traitement.psychologue.fullName }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Date d√©but :</span>
            <span>{{ traitement.dateDebut|date('d/m/Y') }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Date fin :</span>
            <span>{{ traitement.dateFin ? traitement.dateFin|date('d/m/Y') : 'Non d√©finie' }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Statut :</span>
            <span>{{ traitement.statut }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Type :</span>
            <span>{{ traitement.type }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Cat√©gorie :</span>
            <span>{{ traitement.categorie }}</span>
        </div>
        
        <h4 style="margin-top: 15px; color: #28a745;">OBJECTIF TH√âRAPEUTIQUE</h4>
        <p>{{ traitement.objectifTherapeutique|default('Non d√©fini') }}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="info-section">
        <h3>üìä HISTORIQUE DES SUIVIS</h3>
        {% if suivis|length > 0 %}
            <table class="suivi-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Date</th>
                        <th>Type</th>
                        <th>Progression</th>
                        <th>Notes</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for suivi in suivis %}
                        <tr>
                            <td>{{ suivi.dateSuivi|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</td>
                            <td>
                                {% if suivi.valide %}Valid√©
                                {% elseif suivi.effectue %}Effectu√©
                                {% elseif suivi.isEnRetard() %}En retard
                                {% elseif suivi.isAujourdhui() %}Aujourd'hui
                                {% elseif suivi.isAVenir() %}√Ä venir
                                {% else %}Standard{% endif %}
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                {% if suivi.evaluation %}{{ suivi.evaluation * 10 }}%
                                {% elseif suivi.valide %}100%
                                {% elseif suivi.effectue %}80%
                                {% else %}50%{% endif %}
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                {% if suivi.observations %}Patient: {{ suivi.observations|slice(0, 30) }}{% endif %}
                                {% if suivi.observationsPsy %} | Psy: {{ suivi.observationsPsy|slice(0, 30) }}{% endif %}
                                {% if suivi.ressenti %} | Ressenti: {{ suivi.ressenti }}{% endif %}
                                {% if not suivi.observations and not suivi.observationsPsy and not suivi.ressenti %}-{% endif %}
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        {% else %}
            <p>Aucun suivi enregistr√©</p>
        {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <h3>‚úçÔ∏è SIGNATURES OBLIGATOIRES</h3>
        
        <div class="signature-grid">
            <div class="signature-block">
                <h4>SIGNATURE DU PATIENT</h4>
                <div class="signature-line"></div>
                <p><strong>{{ traitement.etudiant.fullName }}</strong></p>
                <p>Date: 
                    <div class="date-field" style="display: inline-block; width: 80px;"></div>
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="signature-block">
                <h4>SIGNATURE DU PSYCHOLOGUE</h4>
                <div class="signature-line"></div>
                <p><strong>{{ traitement.psychologue.fullName }}</strong></p>
                <p>Date: 
                    <div class="date-field" style="display: inline-block; width: 80px;"></div>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="official-stamp">
            TAMPON<br>OFFICIEL<br>UNIMIND
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="validation-section">
        <h4>‚úÖ VALIDATION DU TRAITEMENT</h4>
        <p><em>Cocher les cases appropri√©es</em></p>
        
        <div class="checkbox-grid">
            <div class="checkbox-item">
                <div class="checkbox"></div>
                <span>Traitement termin√© avec succ√®s</span>
            </div>
            <div class="checkbox-item">
                <div class="checkbox"></div>
                <span>Traitement en cours</span>
            </div>
            <div class="checkbox-item">
                <div class="checkbox"></div>
                <span>Objectifs atteints</span>
            </div>
            <div class="checkbox-item">
                <div class="checkbox"></div>
                <span>Objectifs partiels</span>
            </div>
            <div class="checkbox-item">
                <div class="checkbox"></div>
                <span>Suivi satisfaisant</span>
            </div>
            <div class="checkbox-item">
                <div class="checkbox"></div>
                <span>N√©cessite un suivi compl√©mentaire</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 15px;">
            <h4>OBSERVATIONS SUPPL√âMENTAIRES</h4>
            <div class="observations-area"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p><strong>DOCUMENT OFFICIEL - G√âN√âR√â LE {{ "now"|date('d/m/Y H:i:s')|upper }}</strong></p>
        <p>UniMind - Suivi Psychologique - {{ "now"|date('Y') }}</p>
        <p>Ce document est confidentiel et ne peut √™tre utilis√© que par les personnes autoris√©es</p>
        <p>Page 1/2</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
